MGL reports initially processed gravimetry data in two distinct files that share a common format.
Files with names beginning in "MGL-dgsdata" follow the format provided in the MGL_DGS_data.pdf exactly.
Files with names beginning in "AT1A-44" and ending in the file extension ".dat" follow the format provided in the MGL_DGS_data.pdf but are missing the tag (dgsdata) and timestamp added by the LDS logger at the beginning of each line.
